<p>Zendaya showed off the ensemble before the awards show, doing a twirl for a video on her Instagram Story.  </p>

<p>Winners were visited at home by award presenters in black tuxedo-style hazmat gear, designed specially for the event.</p>

<p>For the first time in its 72-year history, this year's show was telecast from the homes of presenters, nominees and winners around the world, keeping with COVID-19 safety protocols. </p>

<p>Host Jimmy Kimmel recorded live from a studio in Downtown Los Angeles, while producers sent more than 150 video kits to other talent, for them to record from home.</p>

